So this is what it was.

01:47:25.000 --> 01:47:29.999
Wow.

01:47:30.000 --> 01:47:37.999
Wow, their voices are so beautiful.

01:47:38.000 --> 01:47:38.999
Wow!

01:47:39.000 --> 01:47:39.999
Wow!

01:47:40.000 --> 01:47:40.999
Wow!

01:47:41.000 --> 01:49:43.999
Wow!

