01:51:31.000 --> 01:51:32.999
It's giving me a lot to think about.

01:51:33.000 --> 01:51:36.999
Right. Let's play it again as today's final song.

01:51:37.000 --> 01:51:38.999
Let's do that.

01:51:39.000 --> 01:51:44.999
—So many thoughts...
—That was wonderful.

01:51:45.000 --> 01:51:46.999
First of all, thank you so much.

01:51:47.000 --> 01:51:48.999
