01:52:19.000 --> 01:52:19.999
Exactly, not saying anything...

01:52:20.000 --> 01:52:20.999
I know.

01:52:21.000 --> 01:52:25.999
Nobody said a word, even on Bubble, so I had no idea.

01:52:26.000 --> 01:52:29.999
Right, I mean, I...

01:52:30.000 --> 01:52:32.999
What was it on Bubble?

01:52:33.000 --> 01:52:37.999
They did mention “12:32.”

01:52:38.000 --> 01:52:38.999
What did they say?

01:52:39.000 --> 01:52:41.999
That they were practicing that song.

01:52:42.000 --> 01:52:43.999
That the song was difficult.

01:52:44.000 --> 01:52:46.999
—They were practicing it.
—Right, I saw that, so I...

01:52:47.000 --> 01:52:48.999
I had absolutely no idea.

01:52:49.000 --> 01:52:49.999
So I looked it up.

01:52:50.000 --> 01:52:53.999
I saw something was happening, but didn't know what.

01:52:54.000 --> 01:52:54.999
I wondered, “What is this?”

01:52:55.000 --> 01:52:57.999
I figured it was for something else.

01:52:58.000 --> 01:53:00.999
I thought it was unrelated to us.

01:53:01.000 --> 01:53:02.999
Then I completely forgot about it.

01:53:03.000 --> 01:53:04.999
There were Bubble messages about practicing it,

01:53:05.000 --> 01:53:06.999
