01:53:07.000 --> 01:53:08.999
Right, right.

01:53:09.000 --> 01:53:11.999
at one of our shows—or at karaoke—

01:53:12.000 --> 01:53:16.999
they could practice singing along.

01:53:17.000 --> 01:53:17.999
I personally had no idea.

01:53:18.000 --> 01:53:19.999
I didn't know it was for this either.

01:53:20.000 --> 01:53:21.999
Because none of us knew,

01:53:22.000 --> 01:53:24.999
—I think PLLI will love it even more.
—Right. If we'd known...

01:53:25.000 --> 01:53:27.999
The surprise was a complete success.

01:53:28.000 --> 01:53:29.999
A complete success.

01:53:30.000 --> 01:53:31.999
To receive a gift like this...

01:53:32.000 --> 01:53:35.999
