01:53:49.000 --> 01:53:52.999
We went to Asterum Café 433-10 yesterday, remember?

01:53:53.000 --> 01:53:54.999
And there...

01:53:55.000 --> 01:53:56.999
PLLI...

01:53:57.000 --> 01:54:00.999
