01:54:22.000 --> 01:54:23.999
Then, while listening to this song,

01:54:24.000 --> 01:54:26.999
it overlapped with those thoughts from yesterday

01:54:27.000 --> 01:54:29.999
and gave me a lot to think about.

01:54:30.000 --> 01:54:33.999
So many thoughts are coming to mind.

01:54:34.000 --> 01:54:35.999
Honestly...

01:54:36.000 --> 01:54:36.999
Their voices are so beautiful.

01:54:37.000 --> 01:54:38.999
Their voices really are beautiful.

01:54:39.000 --> 01:54:39.999
I love you so—

01:54:40.000 --> 01:54:46.999
makes my heart feel all soft.

01:54:47.000 --> 01:54:48.999
Thank you.

