02:16:18.000 --> 02:16:23.999
It's a choir of angels.

02:16:24.000 --> 02:16:25.999
I feel like nothing bad could happen.

02:16:26.000 --> 02:16:27.999
Seriously.

02:16:28.000 --> 02:16:29.999
I feel purified.

02:16:30.000 --> 02:16:34.999
So pure.

02:16:35.000 --> 02:16:36.999
They paid attention to the details.

02:16:37.000 --> 02:16:38.999
They switch to full voice for the rap part.

02:16:39.000 --> 02:16:40.999
