02:16:48.000 --> 02:16:49.999
Wow.

02:16:50.000 --> 02:17:07.999
Even those details...

02:17:08.000 --> 02:17:13.999
This part is difficult.

02:17:14.000 --> 02:17:47.999
They're really good.

02:17:48.000 --> 02:17:55.999
Wow, even the harmonies.

02:17:56.000 --> 02:18:00.999
