—Seriously, thank you.

02:18:12.000 --> 02:18:13.999
Whenever I can't sleep.

02:18:14.000 --> 02:18:16.999
If I fall asleep to this, I don't think I'll have nightmares.

02:18:17.000 --> 02:18:17.999
Oh!

02:18:18.000 --> 02:18:18.999
