02:18:22.000 --> 02:18:23.999
But if I fall asleep to this,

02:18:24.000 --> 02:18:24.999
No nightmares at all.

02:18:25.000 --> 02:18:25.999
It would be so soothing.

02:18:26.000 --> 02:18:29.999
If you still have a nightmare after hearing PLLI's voices,

02:18:30.000 --> 02:18:30.999
