02:18:32.000 --> 02:18:35.999
—No, until you can't even dream...
—Report it to Yejun-hyung?

02:18:36.000 --> 02:18:37.999
I'll put you through a workout.

02:18:38.000 --> 02:18:40.999
Now you're even a certified insomnia therapist.

02:18:41.000 --> 02:18:43.999
—Is there anything you can't do?
—How many qualifications do you have now?

02:18:44.000 --> 02:18:45.999
—Even cosmetology.
—There are too many to count.

02:18:46.000 --> 02:18:47.999
Seriously.

02:18:48.000 --> 02:18:48.999
All right, so...

02:18:49.000 --> 02:18:50.999
And a third-degree black belt in taekwondo.

02:18:51.000 --> 02:18:51.999
My third-degree belt is real!

02:18:52.000 --> 02:18:52.999
Oh, really?

02:18:53.000 --> 02:18:53.999
Do you do kendo too?

02:18:54.000 --> 02:18:54.999
No, I don't do kendo.

02:18:55.000 --> 02:18:56.999
