02:18:57.000 --> 02:18:57.999
At least you're not lying.

02:18:58.000 --> 02:18:58.999
As for kendo...

02:18:59.000 --> 02:18:59.999
I'd be good at it if I tried.

02:19:00.000 --> 02:19:00.999
Of course you would.

02:19:01.000 --> 02:19:02.999
I'd be good if I learned. I've probably got the talent.

02:19:03.000 --> 02:19:05.999
Hi-yah!

02:19:06.000 --> 02:19:07.999
Okay.

02:19:08.000 --> 02:19:08.999
All right, then.

02:19:09.000 --> 02:19:11.999
Great. But if we end like this, we'll lose the emotional mood.

02:19:12.000 --> 02:19:13.999
Let's change the tone again.

02:19:14.000 --> 02:19:17.999
All right, PLLI.

02:19:18.000 --> 02:19:20.999
We ended up receiving such an incredible gift.

02:19:21.000 --> 02:19:22.999
We were the ones who received a gift instead,

02:19:23.000 --> 02:19:25.999
