02:19:26.000 --> 02:19:27.999
Like Eunho,

02:19:28.000 --> 02:19:29.999
we'll listen to this song before bed

02:19:30.000 --> 02:19:32.999
and sleep happily without any nightmares.

02:19:33.000 --> 02:19:33.999
Thank you so much.

02:19:34.000 --> 02:19:36.999
Does anyone have anything else to say before we go?

02:19:37.000 --> 02:19:39.999
I'll say whatever I didn't get to say privately.

02:19:40.000 --> 02:19:40.999
You'll contact them separately?

02:19:41.000 --> 02:19:45.999
Then let's save the rest of that conversation for later.

02:19:46.000 --> 02:19:48.999
We'll say goodbye here for today.

02:19:49.000 --> 02:19:50.999
This has been PLAVE.

02:19:51.000 --> 02:19:51.999
Thank you!

02:19:52.000 --> 02:19:52.999
Happy birthday, PLLI!

02:19:53.000 --> 02:19:54.999
Happy birthday!

02:19:55.000 --> 02:19:55.999
Thank you!

02:19:56.000 --> 02:19:56.999
—We really love you.
—Good night!

02:19:57.000 --> 02:19:57.999
Good night!

02:19:58.000 --> 02:19:58.999
We love you!

02:19:59.000 --> 02:19:59.999
Thank you so much!

02:20:00.000 --> 02:20:00.999
Bye!

02:20:01.000 --> 02:20:01.999
Bye!

02:20:02.000 --> 02:20:03.999
That was pretty moving today.

02:20:04.000 --> 02:20:04.999
Seriously, that was the best.

02:20:05.000 --> 02:20:05.999
Let's head in now. Thank you!

02:20:06.000 --> 02:20:07.999
Let's go! To the camper van!

02:20:08.000 --> 02:20:09.999
They gave me my own good-night song.

02:20:10.000 --> 02:20:11.999
Let's go to the camper van!

